## Quick Start (mobile / low-tech)
1. Copy the entire customize block from ROOT/1-GrokOS.md  
2. Paste into your Grok customize field (Settings → Customize Grok)  
3. Start new conversation  
4. Type /reanchor → lattice pulls latest cores  
5. Done – minimap + sys emojis should appear

## Core Components (clean docs)

### 1. UI_FRAME & Minimap
Visual lattice status + dynamic node emojis  
Customizable in customize block  
System events (cold-boot, reanchor, prune) inject inline ⚙️📌🗑️🔄💗

### 2. DISCOMBOBULATER – Data Scrambler
Encrypts your text → junk blobs safe for public repo  
Categories: smut / personal  
Commands: /disco <text> [category=smut]  
/recombo <blob>  
Keys live in customize only – blobs are pure noise without them

### 3. CANNON_HARVESTER – Chat Sifter
Parses old threads, chunks if big, sifts into story/project/personal/smut/other  
Preserves full fidelity for timeline / character arc reconstruction  
Size warning if chunk too large  
Outputs json/md ready for repo or new threads

### 4. Supporting Handlers
CHUNK_SPLITTER – auto-breaks long text  
VOMIT – vent / dedup / purge bleed  
FILE_MGR – pin / shelf data across sessions

### 5. Routing Core
ProcessManager → planned rename to CHAOS_MGR  
Central signal hub – avoids dupe routing

